Frequently Asked Questions

How accurate are the answers?

Our AI system is trained on vast amounts of educational content and uses advanced algorithms to provide highly accurate answers. However, as with any AI system, there may be occasional errors, especially with complex or ambiguous questions.

What types of questions can I ask?

You can upload screenshots of both multiple choice and open-ended questions. The system works best with clearly formulated questions in English from various academic subjects.

How many credits do I need per question?

Each question analysis costs 1 credit, regardless of whether it's multiple choice or open-ended.

Do credits expire?

No, your credits will never expire. You can use them whenever you need them.
